## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a2ca4-102"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> 允许从宿主应用程序设置状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2ca4-102">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> allows for setting the state from the host application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a2ca4-103">这将使主机应用程序能够重写状态机的当前状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2ca4-103">This enables the host application to override the current state of a state machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a2ca4-104">为此，可以将 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> 类的一个实例排入由常量 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名的 WorkflowQueue 队列中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2ca4-104">This can be accomplished by enqueuing an instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> class to the WorkflowQueue named by the constant <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a2ca4-105">完成此操作的较为简便的方法是使用 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> 类中的 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2ca4-105">A simpler way to accomplish this is to use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method in the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a2ca4-106">可以使用 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> 方法从宿主执行 SetState 操作，或者可以通过将事件排入状态机工作流来亲自执行此操作，如下面的示例所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2ca4-106">You can use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method to perform a SetState operation from the host, or you can do it yourself by enqueuing an event to the state machine workflow as shown in the following example.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void SetState(string targetStateName)  
{  
      if (targetStateName == null)  
      {  
            throw new ArgumentNullException("targetStateName");  
      }  
      SetStateEventArgs args1 = new SetStateEventArgs(targetStateName);  
      this.WorkflowInstance.EnqueueItemOnIdle("SetStateQueue", args1, null, null);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a2ca4-107">状态机工作流使用名为 `SetStateQueue` 的特殊队列来侦听这些特殊事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2ca4-107">The state machine workflow uses a special queue called `SetStateQueue` to listen to these special events.</span></span>
